data.description: Take a look at this 3 Bed, 2.5 Bath, Office, 2 Car Garage, and 2 Car 30x30 Workshop!  Home sits on 1.4 acres in a cul-de-sac in the highly sought after Summerfield Addition.  New Roof, New Heat / Air, New carpet and tile,  New water softener.  The home is great for entertaining Family and Friends with a Large living with see through Fireplace into the Dining.  Step saver Kitchen with Island, Breakfast Bar, plenty of storage and a pantry.  The Master Suite is well designed with Walk-in Closet, Tub, Shower, and Duel Vanities.  All bedrooms have Walk-in Closets and Ceiling Fans.  There's a Covered Patio that opens up to a wide open Backyard that you could create any type of Landscaping, Gardening, or a Pool.  The Workshop is also plumbed for a restroom, with just a little TLC this could be the dream home you've been looking for!  Seller is negotiable.
